<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>7350</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>11898</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>相信每个人都听说过因纽特人。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11899</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>19062</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们住在加拿大、俄罗斯、格陵兰岛和阿拉斯加州。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>19063</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>22781</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大部分因纽特人是猎人。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>22782</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>27123</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们不断地搬家。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>27124</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>33115</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们捕食海豹、海象和鲸鱼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>33116</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>38386</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是，要找到这些动物并不容易。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>38387</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>47377</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有时要花好几个小时，有时甚至要花好几天。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>47378</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>54713</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>冬天捕猎的时候，我们需要一个温暖的住所。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>54714</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>58232</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我的祖先发明了雪屋。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>58233</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>61510</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>雪屋是由雪做成的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>61511</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>67579</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我和爸爸会告诉大家如何建造一个雪屋。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>67580</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>71404</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>首先，你需要做雪块。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>71405</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>77843</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>雪必须足够硬，否则很难做成雪屋。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>77844</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>87531</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>切几个又大又重的雪块，它们将被用于屋子的底部。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>87532</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>91492</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>用铲子做雪块的样子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>91493</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>96449</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>雪块的顶端要按照一定的角度来切。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>96450</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>103594</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这样，雪块堆到最后就会形成一个圆圆的屋顶。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>103595</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>106428</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>把雪块围成一圈。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>106429</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>111852</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>用两个雪块做门，再用一个雪块做门顶。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>111853</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>115764</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>把雪屋地上的雪铲出来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>115765</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>124980</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>现在雪屋的空间更加充足，屋内也会更加暖和了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>124981</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>129129</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>顶部用小一点的雪块。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>129130</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>134526</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在搭建的过程中继续铲雪。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>134527</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>141521</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>现在雪屋看起来像一个小圆顶。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>141522</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>147170</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>进入雪屋，把剩下的几个雪块放好。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>147171</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>151896</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>接下来，用雪塞满所有的缝隙。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>151897</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>157960</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，用你的手把墙抹平。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>157961</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>161648</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>雪屋的门也必须要有角度。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>161649</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>168975</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>为了防止冷空气吹进去，门必须深埋在雪里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>168976</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>175193</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这样做也可以阻挡熊那样的不速之客。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>175194</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>179983</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>现在我们的雪屋建好了！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>179984</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>186605</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>为了方便做饭，爸爸在屋顶钻了一个洞。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>186606</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>188927</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>不过不用担心！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>188928</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>192046</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>火是不会融化雪屋的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>192047</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>199142</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一旦热空气上升，外部的冷空气就会将它冷却下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>199143</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>202929</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>雪块会变得更加坚硬。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>202930</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>206163</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们用鲸脂生火。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>206164</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>208634</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鱼是我的最爱。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>208635</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>212266</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们坐在动物的皮毛上吃东西。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>212267</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>216644</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>雪屋里又温暖又舒适。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>216645</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>222393</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>好好睡了一觉之后，我们又准备去打猎了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>222394</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>227783</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>对于因纽特人来说，建造一个雪屋很快。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>227784</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>234127</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有了雪屋，我们就能在严寒下生存了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>234128</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>243289</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我的祖先发挥聪明智慧，发明了在打猎时可以居住的独特的住处。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>243290</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>249743</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>作为住在雪屋的因纽特人，我感到非常自豪。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>249744</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>254241</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>神奇的雪屋！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>